Interface IMasterTask<E,H>

  • Type Parameters:
    H - The generic type of the value returned by the Callable for the master (the statistics object).
    E - The generic type of the elements in the chunks stored in the BlockingBuffer.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractMasterTask, AbstractPendingSetMasterTask, IndexWriteTask, IndexWriteTask.M, MockMaster

    public interface IMasterTask<E,H>
    Interface for task consuming data written on an application on an asynchronous write buffer.
